                     go to stp-pie-slc-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Reintestazione                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   stp-rei-slc-000      thru stp-rei-slc-999        .
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to stp-pie-slc-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
