      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      120                  to   p-car                  .
           add       1                    to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-prs-pos-ese        to   p-pos                  .
