      *              * Ottenimento record [sct]                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "GK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CLINMS    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      w-slc-cod-cli        to   rf-sct-cod-cli         .
